OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStill the
OL,6,Fodd shower possible this evening, then
OL,7,Fbecoming dry with some good clear
OL,8,Fspells developing tonight. Quite cold
OL,9,Fwith perhaps a touch of frost in
OL,10,Fsheltered spots.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA mainly dry day with some
OL,13,Fbright or sunny intervals and variable
OL,14,Fcloud, the best of the sunshine around
OL,15,Fthe coasts. One or two showers are
OL,16,Fpossible. A colder day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
